Redis 软件的主机配置
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
Redis 软件受主机的内核参数的影响, 这些内核参数登记在下述配置文件:

    •  资源限制文件 /etc/security/limits.conf
    •  资源限制文件 /etc/security/limits.d/20-nproc.conf (优先级高于 /etc/security/limits.conf 资源限制文件)
    •  内核参数文件 /etc/sysctl.conf
    •  启动参数文件 /etc/default/grub (永久关闭透明大页的启动参数 transparent_hugepage=never)

资源限制文件 /etc/security/limits.conf
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
*  -  nproc   65535
*  -  nofile  65535
*  -  core    unlimited
*  -  fsize   unlimited
*  -  rss     unlimited
*  -  stack   unlimited
*  -  memlock unlimited
*  -  as      unlimited

内核参数文件 /etc/sysctl.conf
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
net.core.somaxconn = 65535
net.core.netdev_max_backlog = 65535
net.ipv4.tcp_max_syn_backlog = 65535
net.ipv4.tcp_fin_timeout = 10
net.ipv4.tcp_tw_reuse = 1
net.ipv4.tcp_keepalive_time = 300
vm.overcommit_memory = 1
vm.swappiness = 1
vm.zone_reclaim_mode = 0
fs.file-max = 65535

启动参数文件 /etc/default/grub
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX="... transparent_hugepage=never"

""""""""" 演示资源调优的基本步骤
[root ~]# cat > /etc/security/limits.conf << EOF
*  -  nproc   65535
*  -  nofile  65535
*  -  core    unlimited
*  -  fsize   unlimited
*  -  rss     unlimited
*  -  stack   unlimited
*  -  memlock unlimited
*  -  as      unlimited
EOF
[root ~]# ulimit -a
